channel.title: Making Models for free
channel.description:
Hi, my name is Kevin and I'm sorta new to Making models.. So I need to practice on you guys. =] I will be making models for free for me to practice on. Don't worry, if you like it, you keep it and you put it in your server. Fill out this:
UserName: Color/Colors: Name of Model: Cape : (YES OR NO) Weapon: (YES OR NO) Model/Building: (YES OR NO) Place to wield: (NECK,TORSO,LEGS,HELMET,WEAPON,BOOTS,GLOVES,CAPE)
Please I need to practice and I will have them ready within 1 hour of your order.
